%% streams-pipeline — durable event streams (offline Mermaid source for streams-pipeline.svg)
flowchart LR
  subgraph Producers
    Svc["Services"]
    Saga["Sagas"]
    Trig["Triggers"]
  end

  Log["Append-only log<br/>offset n, n+1, n+2"]
  Store[("Durable store<br/>KV / Prisma")]

  Svc -->|append| Log
  Saga -->|append| Log
  Trig -->|append| Log
  Log --> Store

  subgraph Subscriptions
    A["Consumer A"]
    B["Consumer B"]
    C["Consumer C"]
  end

  Log -->|at-least-once| A
  Log -->|at-least-once| B
  Log -->|at-least-once| C
